content.text:
I'll acknowledge this warmup message. I'm ready to help you explore the codebase and design implementation plans for this box-with-triangular-hole project. I can see this is a multi-implementation CAD project with both FreeCAD and Fornjot (Rust) versions.

I understand my role is strictly read-only - I can explore the codebase using Glob, Grep, Read, and read-only Bash commands, but I cannot create, modify, or delete any files.

What would you like me to help you plan or explore?
